Invocation Name: d. p. s. radio
des: Step back in time and immerse yourself in the golden age of urban music with our radio station dedicated to old-school hip-hop and R&B. From the smooth sounds of R&B crooners like Marvin Gaye and Aretha Franklin to the hard-hitting beats of hip-hop legends like Run-DMC and LL Cool J, we're bringing you the best of the '80s and '90s. Whether you're reminiscing about the days of boomboxes and block parties or discovering these classic tracks for the first time, our station is your destination for authentic, soulful music that continues to inspire and influence artists today. Tune in and let the nostalgia flow as we take you on a journey through the roots of urban music.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
